KDBUr 'aPhUrYM UrThTh NSh'a HV'a BYShUr'aL VY'aShM BB'yL VYMTh.
V'yThH YVSPhV LChT'a VY'yShV LHM MSKH MKSPhM KThBVNM 'yTShBYM M'yShH ChUrShYM KLH LHM HM 'aMUrYM ZBChY 'aDM 'yGLYM YShQVN.
LKN YHYV K'yNN-BQUr VKTL MShKYM HLK KMTSh YS'yUr MGUrN VK'yShN M'aUrBH.
V'aNKY YHVH 'aLHYK M'aUrTSh MTShUrYM V'aLHYM ZVLThY L'a ThD'y VMVShY'y 'aYN BLThY.
'aNY YD'yThYK BMDBUr B'aUrTSh ThL'aBVTh.
KMUr'yYThM VYShB'yV ShB'yV VYUrM LBM 'yL-KN ShKChVNY.
V'aHY LHM KMV-ShChL KNMUr 'yL-DUrK 'aShVUr.
'aPhGShM KDB ShKVL V'aQUr'y SGVUr LBM V'aKLM ShM KLBY'a ChYTh HShDH ThBQ'yM.
ShChThK YShUr'aL KY-BY B'yZUrK.
'aHY MLKK 'aPhV'a VYVShY'yK BKL-'yUrYK VShPhTYK 'aShUr 'aMUrTh ThNH-LY MLK VShUrYM.
'aThN-LK MLK B'aPhY V'aQCh B'yBUrThY.
TShUrVUr 'yVN 'aPhUrYM TShPhVNH ChT'aThV.
ChBLY YVLDH YB'aV LV HV'a-BN L'a ChKM KY-'yTh L'a-Y'yMD BMShBUr BNYM.
MYD Sh'aVL 'aPhDM MMVTh 'aG'aLM 'aHY DBUrYK MVTh 'aHY QTBK Sh'aVL NChM YSThUr M'yYNY.
KY HV'a BN 'aChYM YPhUrY'a YBV'a QDYM UrVCh YHVH MMDBUr 'yLH VYBVSh MQVUrV VYChUrB M'yYNV HV'a YShSH 'aVTShUr KL-KLY ChMDH.
Th'aShM ShMUrVN KY MUrThH B'aLHYH BChUrB YPhLV 'yLLYHM YUrTShV VHUrYVThYV YBQ'yV.
